Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.53,0:00:30.11,Track,,0,0,0,,{\fscx200\fscy140\fade(300,300)}♪{\fscx100\fscy100}Avarice (Kebyou Ningen Track 10)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(400,400)}Oh, I see now.\NYou've lost your way, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(400,400)}I don't know who you are,\Nbut you're quite the unfortunate sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.14,0:00:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(400,400)}Well, this might just be perfect.\NI, too, was set upon by boredom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx115\fscy115\fade(400,400)}Which makes us a pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.69,0:00:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(400,400)}Why do you look so surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.36,0:00:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(400,400)}I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(400,400)}You consider the world you live in...\Nboring, do you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.00,0:00:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(400,400)}As such, you arrived upon this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(400,400)}Oh, please, stop giving me that look.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.77,0:01:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(400,400)}The number of reasons one could have for coming to Ripica's place\N is not within reasonable bounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.64,0:01:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(400,400)}It's simple, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(400,400)}Humans don't know what they should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.65,0:01:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(400,400)}That is why\Nwe continue to take records.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.85,0:01:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(400,400)}Humans are the ones\Nwho upset the balance of the Akashic Records.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.66,0:01:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(400,400)}And the gasoline\Nwhich drives us humans\Nis curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(400,400)}You, for rejecting that fact,\Nare "fakely ill", so to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(400,400)}Yes, how about we call you a "Fakely Ill Human"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.97,0:01:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.6\fade(400,400)\fscx115\fscy115}But come now, do take a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.68,0:01:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.6\fade(400,400)}I don't have any sweets here,\Nbut I can, at the very least, bring out some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx115\fscy115\blur1.6\fade(400,400)}Where is this place, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.68,0:01:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.6\fade(400,400)}Let's be honest:\Ndoes that really matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.12,0:01:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.6\fade(400,400)}So, allow me to get straight to the point.\NWhat sort of story do you wish to hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.19,0:01:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx115\fscy115\blur1.6\fade(400,400)}We only have so much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx115\fscy115\blur1.6\fade(400,400)}What do I mean by "story"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.6\fade(400,400)}Very well.\NShall I choose one for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.6\fade(400,400)}Please wait here momentarily.
