Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.6\fade(400,400)}Please use one of those devices to play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.6\fade(400,400)}Once you do so, perhaps your boring world\Nwill become a little more bearable.
